}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [75.0, 1208.3, 96.8, 1226.1]}, {"text": "Sales of proved reserves in 2018 were related to sales of non-core acreage in the Permian Basin. Sales of proved reserves in 2017 were primarily related to the", "bbox": [112.5, 1208.3, 1157.6, 1226.1]}, {"text": "sale of South Texas.", "bbox": [112.5, 1229.6, 247.2, 1247.3]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [75.0, 1250.9, 96.0, 1268.6]}, {"text": "Approximately 6 percent of the proved developed reserves at December 31, 2018, are nonproducing, primarily associated with Permian EOR.", "bbox": [112.5, 1250.9, 1021.9, 1268.6]}, {"text": "(d)", "bbox": [75.0, 1272.1, 96.8, 1289.8]}, {"text": "Proved undeveloped reserves in the Permian Basin are supported by a five-year detailed field-level development plan, which includes the timing, location and capital", "bbox": [112.5, 1272.1, 1157.6, 1289.8]}, {"text": "commitment of the wells to be drilled. Only proved undeveloped reserves which are reasonably certain to be drilled within five years of booking and are supported", "bbox": [112.5, 1293.4, 1157.6, 1311.1]}, {"text": "by a final investment decision to drill them are included in the development plan. A portion of the proved undeveloped reserves associated with international operations", "bbox": [112.5, 1314.6, 1157.6, 1332.3]}, {"text": "are expected to be developed beyond the five years and are tied to approved long-term development plans.", "bbox": [112.5, 1335.9, 807.2, 1353.6]}, {"text": "Q", "bbox": [527.8, 3.9, 557.5, 41.9]}]}